🫶🏼 @redbullsnow RAILYARD TMMRW :) we 🆙

Day one Tre Squad recap 🙏 congratulations to @breckbensin & @n1ckfox for winning the day 🔥 see you in the finals 🙅🏻‍♂️🧢 thank you @redbullsnow @appterrainpark @recessnc and everyone who came out ❤️ #RedBullRailyard we are loving NC ❤️

Really hard for me to put into words what this weekend meant to me. 
The hospitality and love NC brought to these riders the last few days was some of the raddest sh*t I’ve ever seen. 
I don’t think anyone, especially me, expected how much fun this was going to be. Looking around most of the time everyone had a grin on their face or was hugging their homie. 
I’m so damn grateful for opportunities like this and to include all my friends was the best part. Things like this is what really matters to me in the long run. Results didn’t cuz 
 ALL OF US WERE WINNING. 
These photos and videos just don’t do the energy justice💜
Thankyou @redbullsnow , @notdjcrazylegs @throwingstar_collective Snowboarding , and most importantly the riders & NORTH CAROLINA. 
Btw @n1ckfox up next 🌟
#snowboarding #redbullrailyard #northcarolina

Welp P7🤷🏽‍♂️ ya know how she goes🫠Today was a blast but, couldn’t put 2 down in finals.  So damn hyped to finally do this front 18 in a contest tho😵‍💫
